nomics 啲考試/Assignment都係 Numerical exercise，換言之就好似 Math 1009 咁d/in 同埋簡易嘅 Lagrange Multiplier <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Sem 2 大陸人教好 grade 過 Sem 1</blockquote><br />\n係咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實好 grade 啲嘅都係得 B+ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n常仔你intro micro同macro點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nIntro micro B- , Intro macro B+ <br />\nIntro micro 我諗住Dse 讀過，所以走咗好多堂，勿模仿 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d3c608bdcd9e86daf3c03469078de29413d6cf4","tid":338470,"uid":106958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T14:38:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b32493bae51d467c82ecaf93f528eb1f22f57d4c","tid":338470,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T14:39:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>macro係咪好少數學?都係教d qualitative野?同埋點睇ECON2285,好似教好多野好正,但係會唔會好chur,見個lecturer好似幾好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMacro 好多 Diagram ，其實都係 Model 黎，而背後啲數學有啲深，所以 ug 應該唔會接觸到。教嘅就比較 qualitative ，比較下兩個 model ，試下用個model 去推理咁...<br />\n<br />\n我會 Take ECON2285 ，不過應該 year 4 sem1 先，因為聽講 open book exam... 我睇 course outline 都覺得 chur.."},{"pid":"57a4c3bdfc772a94126635749a35af5c52730490","tid":338470,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T14:43:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽講讀econ嘅都唔會瞓覺</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係，所以我不眠"},{"pid":"602228df5948eb2e3ab66097bf1f42592db532cf","tid":338470,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T14:47:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁之後 econ2210 要睇路</blockquote><br />\n點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nEcon 2210 Intermediate microeconomics 啲考試/Assignment都係 Numerical exercise，換言之就好似 Math 1009 咁d/in 同埋簡易嘅 Lagrange Multiplier <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Sem 2 大陸人教好 grade 過 Sem 1</blockquote><br />\n係咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實好 grade 啲嘅都係得 B+ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n常仔你intro micro同macro點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nIntro micro B- , Intro macro B+ <br />\nIntro micro 我諗住Dse 讀過，所以走咗好多堂，勿模仿 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都讀完micro同macro啦<br />\n啊係喎你好似話過micro係Richard Wong教<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我 micro Hyelim Son 教，不過依家應該冇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> macro 就 Claudian。<br />\n<br />\nCCGL 9018 (Corporate Social Responsibility )就 Richard W. 教，呢個 grade 仲甘，C+ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 從此我就好憎 CSR 呢個 Topic"},{"pid":"226c8d8891688202773693680e370a021b38bf9f","tid":338470,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T14:47:02.000Z","msg":"有<br />\nEcono點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01934fc11f345fb1948d5db401e82dd5b14b51e5","tid":338470,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T14:47:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有<br />\nEcono點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n9月份黎緊都會面對呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我諗依家要執返正啲 stat concept"},{"pid":"0e0161470f411b23b14640f02b0ca357d97a16a3","tid":338470,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T14:48:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>macro係咪好少數學?都係教d qualitative野?同埋點睇ECON2285,好似教好多野好正,但係會唔會好chur,見個lecturer好似幾好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMacro 好多 Diagram ，其實都係 Model 黎，而背後啲數學有啲深，所以 ug 應該唔會接觸到。教嘅就比較 qualitative ，比較下兩個 model ，試下用個model 去推理咁...<br />\n<br />\n我會 Take ECON2285 ，不過應該 year 4 sem1 先，因為聽講 open book exam... 我睇 course outline 都覺得 chur..</blockquote><br />\n咁到時一齊讀,見佢好多calculus of variation<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n下年/yr3補返個intro econ先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"557b8615b4dc7e5ace7e69552cccda54ee51c2bb","tid":338470,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T14:49:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有<br />\nEcono點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n9月份黎緊都會面對呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我諗依家要執返正啲 stat concept</blockquote><br />\n我個stat intro 年半前讀<br />\n個lecturer係無講過proof只講concept<br />\n<br />\n但我econo係同math n econ, qfin一齊讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5def039c5e0f8a6cff71c62310970028b474364","tid":338470,"uid":106958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T14:58:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"61a13792ff2f3c8a9924620f9e7eabd375528c52","tid":338470,"uid":106958,"li